'''佩雷斯·希爾頓'''（{{lang-en|'''Perez Hilton'''}}<ref>{{cite news| url=http://www.nytimes.com/2007/07/29/fashion/29perez.html| title=Love Him or (He Prefers) Hate Him| first=Mireya| last=Navarro| date=July 29, 2007| work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]| accessdate=December 22, 2015| archive-date=2022-04-21| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220421212050/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/07/29/fashion/29perez.html}}</ref>，本名{{lang|en|'''Mario Armando Lavandeira Jr.'''}}，{{bd|1978年|3月23日}}<ref>{{cite web | url = http://perezhilton.com/2012-03-26-perezs-mad-hatter-34th-birthday-bash | title = Perez's Mad Hatter 34th Birthday Bash! | date = March 26, 2012 | publisher = PerezHilton.com | accessdate = December 15, 2013 | archive-date = 2013-12-13 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131213164413/http://perezhilton.com/2012-03-26-perezs-mad-hatter-34th-birthday-bash }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.thehollywoodgossip.com/stars/perez-hilton.html|title=Perez Hilton|work=The Hollywood Gossip|accessdate=March 4, 2015|archive-date=2012-11-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121114112236/http://www.thehollywoodgossip.com/stars/perez-hilton.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是[[美國|美國]]的一位部落格作者、專欄作家和電視主持人。他的部落格內容專門報導名人緋聞<ref>{{cite web|url=http://broadwayworld.com/article/PEREZ_HILTON_DOES_BROADWAY_Yes_THAT_Perez_Hilton_20081017|title=Broadway World|first=Eddie|last=Varley|publisher=BroadwayWorld.com|accessdate=August 23, 2013|archive-date=2012-07-02|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/68qmMldWk?url=http://broadwayworld.com/article/PEREZ_HILTON_DOES_BROADWAY_Yes_THAT_Perez_Hilton_20081017|dead-url=no}}</ref>，並以在名人照片上添加煽情的塗鴉而著稱。希爾頓出生在邁阿密，是一位古巴裔美國人<ref>{{Cite news |date=May 8, 2013 |title=Miami-Born Hollywood Blogger Goes From Nasty To Nice |publisher=[[CBS_Miami|CBS Miami]] |url=http://miami.cbslocal.com/2013/05/08/miami-born-hollywood-blogger-goes-from-nasty-to-nice/ |accessdate=June 24, 2014 |archive-date=2022-04-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220421212111/https://miami.cbslocal.com/2013/05/08/miami-born-hollywood-blogger-goes-from-nasty-to-nice/ }}</ref> ，畢業於[[紐約大學|紐約大學]]<ref>{{Cite news |first=Francisco |last=Alvarado |date=March 27, 2008 |title=Perez Hilton Picks a Fight |newspaper=[[Miami_New_Times|Miami New Times]] |url=http://www.miaminewtimes.com/2008-03-27/news/perez-hilton-picks-a-fight/2/ |accessdate=June 25, 2014 |archive-date=2014-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141101070813/http://www.miaminewtimes.com/2008-03-27/news/perez-hilton-picks-a-fight/2/ }}</ref>。他一度在[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]居住，但已在2013年搬回[[紐約|紐約]]。他是一位已經出櫃的同性戀者。
